@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentBorderColor #546E7A

title The 7 Exploitable Dimensions of EM Modulation

package "CARRIER WAVE: s(t) = A(t) cos[2pi f(t) t + phi(t)]" {

    package "CLASSICAL SCALAR (>85% saturated)" #FFCDD2 {
        component [1. AMPLITUDE  A(t)\nE-field magnitude\n---\nASK, OOK, QAM\n2-12 bits/sym] as AMP
        component [2. PHASE  phi(t)\nAngular position\n---\nBPSK, QPSK, 8PSK\n1-3 bits/sym] as PHASE
        component [3. FREQUENCY  f(t)\nOscillation rate\n---\nFSK, GFSK, OFDM\n1-3 bits/sym + N subs] as FREQ
    }

    package "VECTOR / SPATIAL (40-80% exploited)" #FFE0B2 {
        component [4. POLARISATION\nE-field orientation\n---\nDual-pol Mux\n2x streams] as POL
        component [5. SPATIAL (MIMO)\nAntenna array paths\n---\nMassive MIMO, RIS\nM x streams] as SPATIAL
    }

    package "TOPOLOGICAL (<30% - emerging)" #C8E6C9 {
        component [6. OAM MODE  l\nHelical wavefront twist\n---\nOAM Mux + TIM (proposed)\nN orthogonal modes] as OAM
    }

    package "QUANTUM (<10% - theoretical)" #E1BEE7 {
        component [7. QUANTUM STATE\nCoherent/squeezed photons\n---\nDolinar/Kennedy Rx\nSub-shot-noise] as QSTATE
    }
}

' Combined modulation arrows
AMP -[hidden]right-> PHASE
PHASE -[hidden]right-> FREQ
POL -[hidden]right-> SPATIAL

note bottom of AMP
  QAM combines Amplitude + Phase
  4096-QAM = 12 bits/sym
  ~2 dB from Shannon limit
end note

note bottom of SPATIAL
  Main near-term growth
  5G: 64T64R massive MIMO
  RIS: programmable channel (2030+)
end note

note bottom of OAM
  Highest growth potential
  Infinite orthogonal modes (theory)
  TIM: C(N,K) index bits + K x QAM
end note

note bottom of QSTATE
  Decades from deployment
  But breaks classical noise floor
  6 dB advantage demonstrated (NIST)
end note

legend bottom
|= Colour |= Status |= Headroom |
| <#FFCDD2> | Saturated (>85%) | Diminishing returns |
| <#FFE0B2> | Active frontier (40-80%) | Main growth vector |
| <#C8E6C9> | Emerging (<30%) | Breakthrough potential |
| <#E1BEE7> | Theoretical (<10%) | Paradigm shift |
end legend

@enduml
